674
01:08:57,050 --> 01:09:02,050
Dan kau pikir karena itu
Pak Muhammad membunuh Pak Awzad?

675
01:09:02,217 --> 01:09:03,882
Ya.

676
01:09:04,382 --> 01:09:06,300
Di saat itu...

677
01:09:06,467 --> 01:09:13,925
